About
=====
This is a rebar template for creating erlang special processes, as described in:

 * http://www.erlang.org/doc/design_principles/spec_proc.html
 * http://www.erlang.org/doc/man/proc_lib.html
 * http://www.erlang.org/doc/design_principles/des_princ.html

Tutorials
=========
An article about special processes can be found here:

 * http://erlang.org.ar/ProcesosEspeciales (Spanish)

Installation
============
Just copy simpleproc.template to the priv/templates directory of your rebar
installation.
